{"tid":738474,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"網上瘋傳 A-Z「尼馬字體」！NeyType 成熱門 hashtag","createTime":"2018-07-11T14:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T17:16:15.000Z","uid":32938,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0ef3877294787140065d52e5ed4bf7c31f6ab9","tid":738474,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/221029_310084a6f5578b26b34104d9b9bb7451.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F221029_310084a6f5578b26b34104d9b9bb7451.png&h=53f1f5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界盃將近尾聲，巴西亦早已出局，不過「翻滾尼馬」的熱潮，似乎仍未減退。今日在 Twitter 及 Facebook 等社交網絡，便掀起一陣「尼馬字體」 (Ney Type) 狂潮。由於尼馬跌倒後的姿態甚多，有創作人發現其動作，竟然可以變成 A 至 Z 字，繼而組成不同的詞語。<br />\n<br />\n由世界盃分組賽開始，尼馬誇張的跌倒動作，令不少人「眼前一亮」。一時間，尼馬成為網絡上的熱門題材，各式各樣的改圖改片蜂擁而出。本來以為 8 強巴西出局，熱潮會稍稍減退。想不到今日巴西創作人 Luciano Jacob 發現，尼馬的各種跌倒姿勢，竟然可以變成英文和葡萄牙文字母。第一眼看這張圖，也許覺得沒什麼特別，但當默念 A 至 Z 時，便會發覺似模似樣。<br />\n<br />\nLuciano 稱這為「尼馬字體」 (Ney Type) ，網民看到後都紛紛讚好及分享，並附上 NeyType 這個 hashtag。Luciano 還把圖檔上載至 Dropbox，有興趣的朋友可自行下載。"},{"pid":"e6afad16cfeb0806d6800946209b702ff47ed2fb","tid":738474,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814938efd6bc2ab56ca07fb424a77386a2e5d189","tid":738474,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecc3a21c2e507f51957b51a95da5021300380fc","tid":738474,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e8de48b3558bb0de814a043c65af1c3104b72